nodes.text: In 32 BBY, a male Human served as the Tourist Director of the Tourist Center on Coruscant. That year, Queen Amidala of Naboo and her bodyguard, Captain Quarsh Panaka demanded that the Tourist Director allowed them to access to the company comlinks. They wished to contact the Galactic Senate for assistance after escaping an assassination attempt.
The Tourist Director resembled Agrippa Aldrete, a character whose scenes were cut from Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace.
